-18T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"我在此懇請所有前線撤離，繼續番係度只會送頭。<br />\n而家係不對等武力，前線係絕對無可能推到入去。即使比你入去，都一定係trap，因為佢地知道今次係endgame的最好機會。而家請交比和理非去做，<br />\n而家就算被你救到50人，但要損失100人，咁係咪值得去做丫？（我唔係叫大家散水，但對面的確利用緊我地想救人的心理去不繼拉人；已經拉好多了）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家PPRB班仆街都係咁叫人出黎自首（反映佢地都好急），就係咁，入面的人就守著先，唔好出。如果入面有人道危機，班9都絕對有責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949cdf173af4cfbaf84c952fa663c8a2f2bc0d02","tid":1734122,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:04:25.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"f20d8a8184cb99c886c28c0f4e7308ab6287d1a9","tid":1734122,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"5bba08639dbfd210bccb209fd0aeaab1cc86a413","tid":1734122,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"我知我p牌唔可信<br />\n但簽個名兩秒就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754fd2f5b440651c6555550918c39ed3c6484302","tid":1734122,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"25cb1424cdd3ddb1f04842a55295d9550c6754ce","tid":1734122,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"091590e3ef51eecf20d8dc879214f378d167e3d0","tid":1734122,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"推5"}]}